title: Great Canal Journeys S03E03 PDTV.x264-TVC.mp4
description:
Great Canal Journeys - Series 3, Episode 3




Timothy West and Prunella Scales go to Ireland and travel along the Shannon Erne Waterway, a canal linking the North to the South. Along the way, they try some traditional dancing and folk singing, visit historic sites including Crom Castle and Bloody Pass, and meet a genealogist with a fascinating story to tell. Last in the series.




Original Air Date: 08-Nov-2015
